{"tid":12912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有腸易激綜合症呀？","createTime":"2016-11-30T00:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T21:20:33.000Z","uid":30237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e92e02e861b9369f13b9888b77dc9f14c8a0ff3f","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:22:50.000Z","msg":"有無巴打都有腸易激呀？<br />\n我差唔多次次出街食飯都要搵定廁所咁濟，<br />\n覺得直係好困擾好煩，<br />\n有時又會覺得自己好無用好想喊，<br />\n果次睇醫生問有無藥可以食，點知醫生話無得救，藥都無開比我，<br />\n但係我真係唔想成日咁搵廁所法，<br />\n餐餐都要朋友男友等我<br />\n到底我應該睇腸胃專科定係睇普通家庭醫生先有藥比到我食/改善到？"},{"pid":"66e3e0f1c3d04e640033fa5de0371b9938af0a45","tid":12912,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"我又係食完飯好易肚痛<br />\n<br />\n中學個陣以為係因為身體夠健康<br />\n消化得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概食完半個鐘就有屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9feea17f7cf6c5070e4da5e06bf701fca2903607","tid":12912,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:34:51.000Z","msg":"即是比人嚇一嚇會瀨屎那種人？"},{"pid":"af5b6e3167146873cd1fe8f0cad7a48d705280d7","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T00:42:30.000Z","msg":"樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥"},{"pid":"edb3859b0a135daee086cba1e6d72a8ef91ea7b0","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:00:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我又係食完飯好易肚痛<br />\n<br />\n中學個陣以為係因為身體夠健康<br />\n消化得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大概食完半個鐘就有屎屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你差唔多時間，有時可能過症半個鐘以為無事，點知搭車就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b1c1218326588885296470d1c9f8f2322c5a5f","tid":12912,"uid":8599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:01:34.000Z","msg":"已困擾甚久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244ceb5c01524bec072f80dec3e02d298d92c498","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃鏡腸鏡都照過，無異樣呀<br />\n<br />\n講啦講啦，好想知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6de0653e2d451526cc201dc44f12b2cf9402e5","tid":12912,"uid":22818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:03:13.000Z","msg":"我成日食食下就會急 唔知關唔關心理事"},{"pid":"6604fd1a54d6c52433461427cdc28cbf01d3acd7","tid":12912,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:03:15.000Z","msg":"留名 我朋友最近都有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d5a66d708aa855bda8fc9f4ede0d58e988d553","tid":12912,"uid":31927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:04:36.000Z","msg":"腸易激既人大多有焦慮症狀,你咪心態問題?"},{"pid":"3495b5bf117a7d621e99d664eb84bd46a024762e","tid":12912,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:14:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1cbd722344b099c197ae5b6226d6da3c90828516","tid":12912,"uid":20080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:15:51.000Z","msg":"我都有，好麻煩"},{"pid":"73bb482718277dca4762677caef85246176e2a3e","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:19:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>腸易激既人大多有焦慮症狀,你咪心態問題?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該係，我宜家癲到未食就諗定一陣會唔會又痾，痾又要搵廁所，又要人等，好煩呀咁<br />\n<br />\n我都明應該唔好諗，但係好難囉......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我唔痾我咪唔諗囉，但佢又餐餐都會痾，我咪餐餐淆囉"},{"pid":"269495f4bb99f8ef8ebb86e83dbfee31030283f8","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃鏡腸鏡都照過，無異樣呀<br />\n<br />\n講啦講啦，好想知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶個頭盔先：人人情況唔同，勸各位巴絲有事睇醫生。我唔係醫生，講d野只能做參考。因為我都有呢煩問題，但唔嚴重，唔駛食藥。<br />\n<br />\n首先，IBS 唔會令人增加患癌既機會，亦唔係咩絕症，呢點非常重要，因為病人心理壓力都係會影響病情。只係腸胃容易受食物或情緒刺激，而引起例如肚痾，便秘，胃氣多，肚痛等等症狀。容易為生活帶黎不便。<br />\n<br />\n第一步多數都會叫patient 改善左生活同飲食習慣先，需要時再配合藥物治療。部份人會需要做food allergy testing, 搵出刺激自已腸胃既食物。<br />\nReference (uptodate,做呢行既巴打應該會知道）入面有個食物list參考,會叫patient 試下食少d個種類形既食物睇下有冇改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg&h=5a7a177d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人就係豆類製品，咖啡個d飲完食完即痾。朝早飲一杯咖啡，個肚搞足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔多唔少都會知自已食乜會容易搞肚。<br />\n<br />\n藥既話一陣先講，做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f5c6d24627b53a99c2d9bf46e12c7dbdc62c06b","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃鏡腸鏡都照過，無異樣呀<br />\n<br />\n講啦講啦，好想知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶個頭盔先：人人情況唔同，勸各位巴絲有事睇醫生。我唔係醫生，講d野只能做參考。因為我都有呢煩問題，但唔嚴重，唔駛食藥。<br />\n<br />\n首先，IBS 唔會令人增加患癌既機會，亦唔係咩絕症，呢點非常重要，因為病人心理壓力都係會影響病情。只係腸胃容易受食物或情緒刺激，而引起例如肚痾，便秘，胃氣多，肚痛等等症狀。容易為生活帶黎不便。<br />\n<br />\n第一步多數都會叫patient 改善左生活同飲食習慣先，需要時再配合藥物治療。部份人會需要做food allergy testing, 搵出刺激自已腸胃既食物。<br />\nReference (uptodate,做呢行既巴打應該會知道）入面有個食物list參考,會叫patient 試下食少d個種類形既食物睇下有冇改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg&h=2854311a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人就係豆類製品，咖啡個d飲完食完即痾。朝早飲一杯咖啡，個肚搞足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔多唔少都會知自已食乜會容易搞肚。<br />\n<br />\n藥既話一陣先講，做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFood allergy test以前諗過做，見到浸會有，但果時未出黎做野無錢做，慢慢就無左回事，估唔到對腸易激都有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都大約知道自己飲就奶同咖啡就死硬咁濟，一日三轉走唔甩，但我自己又好中意飲呢類....唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，等你教埋藥果邊可以點做<br />\n我想問下益生菌果類其實有無用？"},{"pid":"1a1fcb0a65f2a2763f5e683ed193328f5cebf760","tid":12912,"uid":1644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即是比人嚇一嚇會瀨屎那種人？</blockquote><br />\n傻尻以為好幽默 =.=</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n表情撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbfecf89f2f87f7993a9fed4ec9c391a14b7cc02","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都有，好麻煩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有無打算做d咩去改善？我唔知點入手好。<br />\n有睇中醫，但係一停中藥又黎返咁...我唔想keep住係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfc2eddd0d086ceccee97a0367552a47af4d1d4","tid":12912,"uid":2899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:55:14.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過試中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5313a75d8c4981e45012d5ce4e8dd70934e7364","tid":12912,"uid":3575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:55:38.000Z","msg":"食親早餐就有得痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90856df12c334e0e169882863218fe8b21cc3174","tid":12912,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T01:55:49.000Z","msg":"我腸胃都幾差 一兩個月都會腸胃炎一次<br />\n不過又唔會日日都係咁想屙 咁係咩病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ce138e4392e0a49e2d703b3fd7a736eb646e82","tid":12912,"uid":7407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:01:02.000Z","msg":"照過腸胃鏡，醫生話無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就成日都好唔舒服，不過我又無成日痾，係有時會便袐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763fd49cd3f5c4ed3b328577132bd33b5a0512ee","tid":12912,"uid":7407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"照過腸胃鏡，醫生話無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就成日條大腸都好唔舒服，不過我又無成日痾，係有時會便袐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070c24444b2422d819b32f649102ef2c3364bdbb","tid":12912,"uid":5319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:08:51.000Z","msg":"我係因為心理壓力有Ibs 照曬腸胃鏡 驗血等等 有胃炎 <br />\n因為個人好易緊張 經常性胃痛引起心口痛 背痛 <br />\n開頭以為就快死 心臟病  做左好多全身檢查無事<br />\n只有信醫生無事啦... 依家似咖啡即死 胃酸倒流 心口痛 成日<br />\n做運動頭暈想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  還在治療中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eacdb8c13033e2d365198c48d567b5869b9a055","tid":12912,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:09:00.000Z","msg":"Ibs 點會無藥食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924e4e2a05ba1e434740aa46718a15d4a730c8fa","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃鏡腸鏡都照過，無異樣呀<br />\n<br />\n講啦講啦，好想知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶個頭盔先：人人情況唔同，勸各位巴絲有事睇醫生。我唔係醫生，講d野只能做參考。因為我都有呢煩問題，但唔嚴重，唔駛食藥。<br />\n<br />\n首先，IBS 唔會令人增加患癌既機會，亦唔係咩絕症，呢點非常重要，因為病人心理壓力都係會影響病情。只係腸胃容易受食物或情緒刺激，而引起例如肚痾，便秘，胃氣多，肚痛等等症狀。容易為生活帶黎不便。<br />\n<br />\n第一步多數都會叫patient 改善左生活同飲食習慣先，需要時再配合藥物治療。部份人會需要做food allergy testing, 搵出刺激自已腸胃既食物。<br />\nReference (uptodate,做呢行既巴打應該會知道）入面有個食物list參考,會叫patient 試下食少d個種類形既食物睇下有冇改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg&h=5a7a177d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人就係豆類製品，咖啡個d飲完食完即痾。朝早飲一杯咖啡，個肚搞足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔多唔少都會知自已食乜會容易搞肚。<br />\n<br />\n藥既話一陣先講，做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFood allergy test以前諗過做，見到浸會有，但果時未出黎做野無錢做，慢慢就無左回事，估唔到對腸易激都有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都大約知道自己飲就奶同咖啡就死硬咁濟，一日三轉走唔甩，但我自己又好中意飲呢類....唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，等你教埋藥果邊可以點做<br />\n我想問下益生菌果類其實有無用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機cut quote 好麻煩，唔cut了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nIBS 分幾型，肚屙型IBS-D，便秘型IBS-C，混合型IBS-M。食藥方法會有d唔同。<br />\n如果便秘型既走去食loperamide(止痾藥）,肯定有排唔駛痾屎。<br />\n<br />\n首先要明白好多藥物都係for relief symptoms, 唔好諗住食完會好返晒，而我都只會講幾款我知道或者食過既藥。好多人調整左飲食模式之後，已經大大改善左，根本唔駛食藥。 總之life style 好重要！<br />\n<br />\n回應樓主情況：<br />\n<br />\nprobiotic-做過study,對IBS冇咩明顯幫助。不過食左冇壞。<br />\n<br />\n肚屙：<br />\n- loperamide (正廠速治靈）正餐前45分鐘食一粒。<br />\n<br />\n- eluxadoline (香港冇，唔多講）<br />\n<br />\n- (5HT-3) antagonist 例如alosetron 同ondansetron,痾到仆街入院先會用。<br />\n<br />\n腸抽筋：<br />\n(部份亦藥對減少胃氣漲有幫助）<br />\n<br />\n- colpermin capsule ,成份：peppermint oil。正餐前30-60分鐘食一粒。呢隻試過regular 食一排，個人效果幾好，冇咁多胃氣同腸痛。<br />\n<br />\n -buscopan 10mg,飯前15分鐘食。<br />\n<br />\n- dicyclomine ( 好多牌子胃藥都會有呢隻成份）<br />\n<br />\n-部份情緒問題導致IBS 既藥我唔講啦，睇醫生會好d。<br />\n<br />\ncolpermin 同埋loperamide 係non poison ,同圍都有得買。<br />\n我自已日日帶住係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/105839_2a4f14d15fcaef88a4d3e8d0aa587a8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F105839_2a4f14d15fcaef88a4d3e8d0aa587a8b.jpg&h=5f6410a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4aa627218d497ebd778c3f36cd00e35e555d97de","tid":12912,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"有懷疑過自己係唔係<br />\n食完嘢會好耐都唔落格，成日嗝番啲氣上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食多少少又肚痛又痾又盛<br />\n個肚就成日脹 睇過醫生 佢又冇講啲咩 淨係話我肚好多氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完化氣藥之後效果都唔大"},{"pid":"c0ce89de831608c6037033c9b594acd19ccd2fd8","tid":12912,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:08:07.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75edf2ba68fa951895a70e8593a1a535f613d33c","tid":12912,"uid":32434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:16:08.000Z","msg":"我同樓主一樣 <br />\n我係一緊張就想柯<br />\n成日凝住會柯 凝凝下就變左真係肚痛<br />\n<br />\n明明係屋企冇事 一出遠小小出事<br />\n<br />\n依家驚左去旅行 點搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過醫生 佢話如果嚴重 要食鎮靜劑<br />\n佢淨係叫我唔好凝住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c1d78aede2ceed9b93680f8df526d4cca4799b","tid":12912,"uid":21950,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:34:57.000Z","msg":"我以前就係試過搭車急到要瀨, 呢種感覺到而家搭緊車小小塞就自然諗起&quot;如果急起上黎點算&quot;呢個念頭, 原本都冇屎癮, 一諗呢樣野個肚就黎黎哋料, 同埋唔知係咪慣左屙屎會whatsapp, 如果個肚黎料而同時whatsapp效果會更加嚴重. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c02bcbd65bcfdf8011815c40f21196aa2f641d","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前就係試過搭車急到要瀨, 呢種感覺到而家搭緊車小小塞就自然諗起&quot;如果急起上黎點算&quot;呢個念頭, 原本都冇屎癮, 一諗呢樣野個肚就黎黎哋料, 同埋唔知係咪慣左屙屎會whatsapp, 如果個肚黎料而同時whatsapp效果會更加嚴重. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nwhatsapp"},{"pid":"8a42296c23fa3229838d8773e147f99d05a2e05f","tid":12912,"uid":33057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:38:36.000Z","msg":"以前一考試就會痛<br />\n考之前冇痾屎就仆街"},{"pid":"bafffbdb91ab6bb5db104f6d566b8f0fbb82b994","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主做晒檢查未，即係腸鏡胃鏡個d?<br />\n要先make sure 唔係其他問題先。<br />\nIBS(腸易激綜合症）有一套treatment guideline , 有d藥可以幫你減輕唔舒服。<br />\n如果你想知我可以講下既<br />\n當然睇專科最穩陣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過醫院藥房配藥</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃鏡腸鏡都照過，無異樣呀<br />\n<br />\n講啦講啦，好想知可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶個頭盔先：人人情況唔同，勸各位巴絲有事睇醫生。我唔係醫生，講d野只能做參考。因為我都有呢煩問題，但唔嚴重，唔駛食藥。<br />\n<br />\n首先，IBS 唔會令人增加患癌既機會，亦唔係咩絕症，呢點非常重要，因為病人心理壓力都係會影響病情。只係腸胃容易受食物或情緒刺激，而引起例如肚痾，便秘，胃氣多，肚痛等等症狀。容易為生活帶黎不便。<br />\n<br />\n第一步多數都會叫patient 改善左生活同飲食習慣先，需要時再配合藥物治療。部份人會需要做food allergy testing, 搵出刺激自已腸胃既食物。<br />\nReference (uptodate,做呢行既巴打應該會知道）入面有個食物list參考,會叫patient 試下食少d個種類形既食物睇下有冇改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F091313_5135ebafc69b01117b4fdf1832377fd1.jpg&h=2854311a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個人就係豆類製品，咖啡個d飲完食完即痾。朝早飲一杯咖啡，個肚搞足成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主唔多唔少都會知自已食乜會容易搞肚。<br />\n<br />\n藥既話一陣先講，做緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFood allergy test以前諗過做，見到浸會有，但果時未出黎做野無錢做，慢慢就無左回事，估唔到對腸易激都有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都大約知道自己飲就奶同咖啡就死硬咁濟，一日三轉走唔甩，但我自己又好中意飲呢類....唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好，等你教埋藥果邊可以點做<br />\n我想問下益生菌果類其實有無用？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手機cut quote 好麻煩，唔cut了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\nIBS 分幾型，肚屙型IBS-D，便秘型IBS-C，混合型IBS-M。食藥方法會有d唔同。<br />\n如果便秘型既走去食loperamide(止痾藥）,肯定有排唔駛痾屎。<br />\n<br />\n首先要明白好多藥物都係for relief symptoms, 唔好諗住食完會好返晒，而我都只會講幾款我知道或者食過既藥。好多人調整左飲食模式之後，已經大大改善左，根本唔駛食藥。 總之life style 好重要！<br />\n<br />\n回應樓主情況：<br />\n<br />\nprobiotic-做過study,對IBS冇咩明顯幫助。不過食左冇壞。<br />\n<br />\n肚屙：<br />\n- loperamide (正廠速治靈）正餐前45分鐘食一粒。<br />\n<br />\n- eluxadoline (香港冇，唔多講）<br />\n<br />\n- (5HT-3) antagonist 例如alosetron 同ondansetron,痾到仆街入院先會用。<br />\n<br />\n腸抽筋：<br />\n(部份亦藥對減少胃氣漲有幫助）<br />\n<br />\n- colpermin capsule ,成份：peppermint oil。正餐前30-60分鐘食一粒。呢隻試過regular 食一排，個人效果幾好，冇咁多胃氣同腸痛。<br />\n<br />\n -buscopan 10mg,飯前15分鐘食。<br />\n<br />\n- dicyclomine ( 好多牌子胃藥都會有呢隻成份）<br />\n<br />\n-部份情緒問題導致IBS 既藥我唔講啦，睇醫生會好d。<br />\n<br />\ncolpermin 同埋loperamide 係non poison ,同圍都有得買。<br />\n我自已日日帶住係身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/105839_2a4f14d15fcaef88a4d3e8d0aa587a8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F105839_2a4f14d15fcaef88a4d3e8d0aa587a8b.jpg&h=2d4a36c1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一陣買返盒傍身先<br />\n我諗自己係混合型掛，一係無屎痾，一係食完飯就即痾<br />\n<br />\n係ibs令我有情緒問題囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你教識我咁多"},{"pid":"28396e452943b00d54d42a2ac656034511cfb3fd","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:10:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我同樓主一樣 <br />\n我係一緊張就想柯<br />\n成日凝住會柯 凝凝下就變左真係肚痛<br />\n<br />\n明明係屋企冇事 一出遠小小出事<br />\n<br />\n依家驚左去旅行 點搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過醫生 佢話如果嚴重 要食鎮靜劑<br />\n佢淨係叫我唔好凝住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫醫生食屎<br />\n我真心諗唔到點唔好凝住者<br />\n我一諗起要去食飯就諗起肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過係大阪食完和牛，行緊返酒店途中（重要四個字路程左右），衝入間餐廳講一大堆すいません再問人借廁所.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69c00e1eeca93c04646b422404f29bbac675a8e7","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:11:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前就係試過搭車急到要瀨, 呢種感覺到而家搭緊車小小塞就自然諗起&quot;如果急起上黎點算&quot;呢個念頭, 原本都冇屎癮, 一諗呢樣野個肚就黎黎哋料, 同埋唔知係咪慣左屙屎會whatsapp, 如果個肚黎料而同時whatsapp效果會更加嚴重. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到whatsapp咁危險"},{"pid":"561445be10a363a988214a8803e710dd69520aa1","tid":12912,"uid":42949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:12:12.000Z","msg":"試過有排好耐都冇柯 好似便秘咁<br />\n之後就變左日日柯 但係柯爛屎<br />\n之後依加又變左好耐冇柯<br />\n但有時柯爛屎 有時又正常一條條<br />\n<br />\n同埋成日放屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b168a89d1435d667027e8df865bbb575c29ca68","tid":12912,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:15:19.000Z","msg":"我有，不過唔係會屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bdadb984ab979cced2bb52b7f2e3e123198a36","tid":12912,"uid":12475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:15:27.000Z","msg":"柯屎係人生最快的時刻呀"},{"pid":"eb8ff81ac82da92237ca1df20c97077235bdbeb8","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:29:46.000Z","msg":"樓主如果係混合型，止痾藥係需要時食，唔好三餐都用，以免令便秘既時間更唔舒服。<br />\n我都係混合，有時情願痾出黎好過谷住。<br />\n我試過谷到個人死咁滯，食唔到野同係咁嘔，d腸好似唔郁咁，差d入醫院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7012744b921d2c602ec07df29489aec9e51aba","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:36:23.000Z","msg":"想同呢個post 既巴絲講返聲，係香港生活真係好大壓力同埋急節奏急速。唔少人腸胃都有一定問題，但唔好輕易自已幫自已斷証，同埋唔好亂食藥，檢查真係好重要。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以嘗試放鬆d個日同埋戒左唔好既飲食習慣。希望大家都痾再健康既香蕉屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dc89b269f49a9dc7a12cf85f9ee6ac6b7d2372","tid":12912,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"留明<br />\n食完實有得痾"},{"pid":"3577db6eb48620550166a0ae781e141f1a6797e7","tid":12912,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6910b4c4e8e25f1382e20c5061b32ebf157e7a7e","tid":12912,"uid":33465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:44:34.000Z","msg":"Duspatalin 135mg"},{"pid":"87d3c1607e920dced962ebf46d2aca8fcb7ca525","tid":12912,"uid":1562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"我都好似有<br />\n食完野就好易急屎<br />\n尤其食午餐後"},{"pid":"d92dfaa5b636866d7778a21a67ecdb8373d02e53","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Duspatalin 135mg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢隻既indication 都係for IBS"},{"pid":"077633b4f2f6cc8cca395a1deff602159a785f4d","tid":12912,"uid":4691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:52:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Duspatalin 135mg</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呢隻既indication 都係for IBS</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n腸抽筋個陣用"},{"pid":"e321ca4c0ec0103708306925fedc803c7b375471","tid":12912,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:53:13.000Z","msg":"樓主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我腸胃都麻麻"},{"pid":"349a36ca86d3f4c4e69d7c51b0c46c0820e342e2","tid":12912,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:54:04.000Z","msg":"之前有一期周不時會腸痛，有時仲痛得幾勁<br />\n我都驚驚地有咩野"},{"pid":"3ba1339175d25f75f936cdd0d02ca7f51fd37081","tid":12912,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"其實嚴格上IBS真係無得醫<br />\n因為絕大部分人覺得有得醫即係可以痊癒<br />\n但其實而家嘅治療<br />\n主要都係啲處理病徵嘅藥<br />\n俗稱嘅頭痛醫頭、腳痛醫腳<br />\n所以樓主位醫生話無得醫都唔可以話錯晒<br />\n<br />\n但IBS呢樣嘢<br />\n最緊要就係病人自己要知道<br />\nIBS好多時會一路陪住你，係長期病<br />\n但就學識點樣改善自己嘅生活，減少日常壓力<br />\n真係有需要就食藥短暫控制病情<br />\n當然如果你有啲抑鬱/焦慮，醫生都可以處方埋情緒藥，但唔係個個啱駛<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下mayo clinic嘅網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/irritable-bowel-syndrome/basics/definition/CON-20024578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Firritable-bowel-syndrome%2Fbasics%2Fdefinition%2FCON-20024578&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=934609db\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/irritable-bowel-syndrome/basics/definition/CON-20024578</a><br />\n<br />\n利申︰黃綠醫生"},{"pid":"b7c23e2763297c723ae023a3539e17bb51e5ffa0","tid":12912,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實嚴格上IBS真係無得醫<br />\n因為絕大部分人覺得有得醫即係可以痊癒<br />\n但其實而家嘅治療<br />\n主要都係啲處理病徵嘅藥<br />\n俗稱嘅頭痛醫頭、腳痛醫腳<br />\n所以樓主位醫生話無得醫都唔可以話錯晒<br />\n<br />\n但IBS呢樣嘢<br />\n最緊要就係病人自己要知道<br />\nIBS好多時會一路陪住你，係長期病<br />\n但就學識點樣改善自己嘅生活，減少日常壓力<br />\n真係有需要就食藥短暫控制病情<br />\n當然如果你有啲抑鬱/焦慮，醫生都可以處方埋情緒藥，但唔係個個啱駛<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以睇下mayo clinic嘅網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/irritable-bowel-syndrome/basics/definition/CON-20024578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mayoclinic.org%2Fdiseases-conditions%2Firritable-bowel-syndrome%2Fbasics%2Fdefinition%2FCON-20024578&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=934609db\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/irritable-bowel-syndrome/basics/definition/CON-20024578</a><br />\n<br />\n利申︰黃綠醫生</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIBS應該有得醫既<br />\nIBS只係個病名，表現出黎就係腹痛、瀉，or 便秘<br />\n但病機各異，可能平日日常無事無幹，本身腸胃都麻麻地...etc<br />\n又要好似偵探咁搵個原因出黎<br />\n我相信有得處理既，不過要診斷得準<br />\n<br />\n利申：庸醫"},{"pid":"471249dcafb0cc0818f11ccf0f66902c5469b221","tid":12912,"uid":32434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我同樓主一樣 <br />\n我係一緊張就想柯<br />\n成日凝住會柯 凝凝下就變左真係肚痛<br />\n<br />\n明明係屋企冇事 一出遠小小出事<br />\n<br />\n依家驚左去旅行 點搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過醫生 佢話如果嚴重 要食鎮靜劑<br />\n佢淨係叫我唔好凝住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫醫生食屎<br />\n我真心諗唔到點唔好凝住者<br />\n我一諗起要去食飯就諗起肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過係大阪食完和牛，行緊返酒店途中（重要四個字路程左右），衝入間餐廳講一大堆すいません再問人借廁所.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰次我係 睇家庭醫生<br />\n可能因為我睇完感冒 搭單問佢腸易激 佢先hea我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次去行山 肚痛 十分無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去日本 韓國城市化既地方都還可以<br />\n叫我再去行個山 郊個遊 真係唔好搞<br />\n搭長途車都驚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下，腸抽筋即係點<br />\nFeel到個肚係咁搞？"},{"pid":"40d74b5ba568ddf82f6f822d26adfb1e5a7ecd81","tid":12912,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IBS應該有得醫既<br />\nIBS只係個病名，表現出黎就係腹痛、瀉，or 便秘<br />\n但病機各異，可能平日日常無事無幹，本身腸胃都麻麻地...etc<br />\n又要好似偵探咁搵個原因出黎<br />\n我相信有得處理既，不過要診斷得準<br />\n<br />\n利申：庸醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但搵到個原因<br />\n嗰個病仲係咪叫IBS呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用emedicine嘅definition<br />\n&quot;Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) is a functional GI disorder characterized by abdominal pain and altered bowel habits in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology, although microscopic inflammation has been documented in some patients.&quot;<br />\nIBS嘅精粹就係&quot;in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology&quot;<br />\n簡單啲就係現今醫學無辦法解釋到嘅病徵<br />\n<br />\n我諗你都係做呢行<br />\n大家都好想make most accurate diagnosis<br />\n奈何有時真係無辦法做到<br />\n或者係現今醫學根本無一個好嘅解釋<br />\n對病人，唯有幫得幾多就幾多"},{"pid":"a03a6fb34743dcb296a1ef407b139944ccdcd862","tid":12912,"uid":5319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IBS應該有得醫既<br />\nIBS只係個病名，表現出黎就係腹痛、瀉，or 便秘<br />\n但病機各異，可能平日日常無事無幹，本身腸胃都麻麻地...etc<br />\n又要好似偵探咁搵個原因出黎<br />\n我相信有得處理既，不過要診斷得準<br />\n<br />\n利申：庸醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但搵到個原因<br />\n嗰個病仲係咪叫IBS呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用emedicine嘅definition<br />\n&quot;Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) is a functional GI disorder characterized by abdominal pain and altered bowel habits in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology, although microscopic inflammation has been documented in some patients.&quot;<br />\nIBS嘅精粹就係&quot;in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology&quot;<br />\n簡單啲就係現今醫學無辦法解釋到嘅病徵<br />\n<br />\n我諗你都係做呢行<br />\n大家都好想make most accurate diagnosis<br />\n奈何有時真係無辦法做到<br />\n或者係現今醫學根本無一個好嘅解釋<br />\n對病人，唯有幫得幾多就幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n胃酸過多 倒流 心口痛 同背痛又可以食咩藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b10487ccf9ab2fc929f3e6d1bf3ff8353ac3a","tid":12912,"uid":13738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IBS應該有得醫既<br />\nIBS只係個病名，表現出黎就係腹痛、瀉，or 便秘<br />\n但病機各異，可能平日日常無事無幹，本身腸胃都麻麻地...etc<br />\n又要好似偵探咁搵個原因出黎<br />\n我相信有得處理既，不過要診斷得準<br />\n<br />\n利申：庸醫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但搵到個原因<br />\n嗰個病仲係咪叫IBS呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用emedicine嘅definition<br />\n&quot;Irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) is a functional GI disorder characterized by abdominal pain and altered bowel habits in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology, although microscopic inflammation has been documented in some patients.&quot;<br />\nIBS嘅精粹就係&quot;in the absence of a specific and unique organic pathology&quot;<br />\n簡單啲就係現今醫學無辦法解釋到嘅病徵<br />\n<br />\n我諗你都係做呢行<br />\n大家都好想make most accurate diagnosis<br />\n奈何有時真係無辦法做到<br />\n或者係現今醫學根本無一個好嘅解釋<br />\n對病人，唯有幫得幾多就幾多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我只係中醫<br />\n中醫既pathology同現代醫學唔同<br />\n無一個病機同一個症狀掛鉤<br />\n所以辨證論治就應該ok<br />\n以往clinical黎講<br />\n好多現代醫學不明原因既病，中醫都處理到<br />\nIBS印象中某U都做左好多research<br />\n不過你講得岩，病人自己都要做好能力範圍既事<br />\n就係管理好情緒"},{"pid":"f7e02f3bac0842d0c1813c7746979ef76d1f7618","tid":12912,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:26:56.000Z","msg":"試下食益生菌，我食左一排由每日痾6，7次減少到痾兩次"},{"pid":"eb10872cba03b62821417843515b3331321e56ec","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:27:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我同樓主一樣 <br />\n我係一緊張就想柯<br />\n成日凝住會柯 凝凝下就變左真係肚痛<br />\n<br />\n明明係屋企冇事 一出遠小小出事<br />\n<br />\n依家驚左去旅行 點搵廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過醫生 佢話如果嚴重 要食鎮靜劑<br />\n佢淨係叫我唔好凝住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫醫生食屎<br />\n我真心諗唔到點唔好凝住者<br />\n我一諗起要去食飯就諗起肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過係大阪食完和牛，行緊返酒店途中（重要四個字路程左右），衝入間餐廳講一大堆すいません再問人借廁所.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n嗰次我係 睇家庭醫生<br />\n可能因為我睇完感冒 搭單問佢腸易激 佢先hea我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次去行山 肚痛 十分無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去日本 韓國城市化既地方都還可以<br />\n叫我再去行個山 郊個遊 真係唔好搞<br />\n搭長途車都驚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想問下，腸抽筋即係點<br />\nFeel到個肚係咁搞？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n話說，我係腸胃炎睇醫生時搭單問<br />\n可能佢係因為咁所以hea我掛<br />\n<br />\n我試過和石山拜緊途中搵廁所.....污糟到癲但又無得唔去，果下真心好嬲自己點解咁<br />\n<br />\n腸抽筋應該係個肚la埋一住咁痛掛<br />\n利申：無試過，我淨係喪痾"},{"pid":"9d911ca57743561d4664bed1d17f8c2135467d50","tid":12912,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:33:13.000Z","msg":"我一定有，係大商場知道有廁所而且廁所都ok就唔會咁易肚痛，但去小店就好易驚到痛、急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f4f1759491aaea83ec918a5b685fe404ac91f3","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下食益生菌，我食左一排由每日痾6，7次減少到痾兩次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去gnc睇，3百幾蚊一個月，但係唔記得帶會員卡就無買"},{"pid":"cb8efa4a546a0f444f4f7b83e824aa3844b224ca","tid":12912,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［突發］美國學者籌旗出粵英詞典！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/7401?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/7401?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\nKickstarter link: <a href=\"http://kck.st/2fjxPNf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkck.st%2F2fjxPNf&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=7ac2e5a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://kck.st/2fjxPNf</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果新聞link<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20161127/19846701\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20161127%2F19846701&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzR3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1e2afe83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Fspecial%2Fart%2F20161127%2F19846701&h=df22f5f7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/special/art/20161127/19846701</a><br />\n<br />\n唔想廣東話就咁消失嘅話就有錢出錢 有力出力 幫手share出去！冇理由身為香港人連自己日日講嘅語言都保護唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6cb928c002b4afa55f2150dbcf63fa4526e72dd3","tid":12912,"uid":18179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>胃酸過多 倒流 心口痛 同背痛又可以食咩藥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n首先要確定你係咪真係胃酸倒流<br />\n先知俾咩藥你<br />\n同埋背痛唔係胃酸倒流嘅常見病徵之一<br />\n建議你去睇睇你嘅家庭醫生<br />\n問完症同做完檢查，先至由佢開返最適合你嘅藥俾你<br />\n<br />\n不過如果只係胃酸問題<br />\n可以考慮去藥房買嘉胃斯康<br />\n有啲病人覺得水劑好過丸劑<br />\n完全無效就更加要盡早睇醫生"},{"pid":"836820608a5025cfd8332d5dceeaf820fe3c8b18","tid":12912,"uid":45123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"已有4年 一食完飯就想去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做人輕鬆啲 會有幫助"},{"pid":"bcf756e4f314add238e59485fd88accb082ac065","tid":12912,"uid":35357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:06:21.000Z","msg":"唔會有便秘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f06520cc06a9c0db7d0b1f10b9ea752bab42be","tid":12912,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"注意飲食就得啦<br />\n一定知有邊啲野食落會痾<br />\n我就是成功的例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c23acba7cbf0f48d3783579e3dc8cdb061708b","tid":12912,"uid":21992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"出現依種情況既巴絲係咪都係瘦底"},{"pid":"cd854c0484d8718246c6d07d0dae62b171ca3ca5","tid":12912,"uid":11827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:27:54.000Z","msg":"你試下搵野食雪藏食物要解凍果隻，如燒野食都係要解凍睇下，睇下之後會唔會勁屙。如果有試下少食呢種食物"},{"pid":"a1a0f77c5541224b615f6e2643ed4d96c3683045","tid":12912,"uid":7940,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:29:03.000Z","msg":"靚女唔痾屎"},{"pid":"1da76a5762ce350f9299fd4bd92f2524e86058f0","tid":12912,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:30:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試下食益生菌，我食左一排由每日痾6，7次減少到痾兩次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去gnc睇，3百幾蚊一個月，但係唔記得帶會員卡就無買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我求其買一隻，百幾二百蚊到"},{"pid":"63d4c8dbbaea10f7e7dff65f3622ee507f211c5d","tid":12912,"uid":42687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:31:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出現依種情況既巴絲係咪都係瘦底</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係，肥到仆街，痾得多好易餓係咁食"},{"pid":"ef8e43d26efbb1dc1e73966e25b2001704cdf2de","tid":12912,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"一有靚女係隔離我就好唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92e1df4e82f1ba500b7aee7812f9a17b8144f204","tid":12912,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無巴打都有腸易激呀？<br />\n我差唔多次次出街食飯都要搵定廁所咁濟，<br />\n覺得直係好困擾好煩，<br />\n有時又會覺得自己好無用好想喊，<br />\n果次睇醫生問有無藥可以食，點知醫生話無得救，藥都無開比我，<br />\n但係我真係唔想成日咁搵廁所法，<br />\n餐餐都要朋友男友等我<br />\n到底我應該睇腸胃專科定係睇普通家庭醫生先有藥比到我食/改善到？</blockquote><br />\n睇腸胃專科啦 唔係專科其實唔係好識<br />\n<br />\n睇私家腸胃專科啦 公立等一年都唔知有冇得睇"},{"pid":"4ba3e900b015ad16db35b63528e0079dfebde050","tid":12912,"uid":37001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:44:04.000Z","msg":"我都有呢類情況，每次食完飯後半粒鐘內一定會感覺到個肚有少少攪攪下就黎出黎咁，最辛苦唔係忍住而係每次食完野都要諗下邊到有廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間唔中食太油既野就會腸胃炎，屋企一定有好幾包腸胃炎既藥看門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681522052991bedce84631b41605ef65dd9a7a2f","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出現依種情況既巴絲係咪都係瘦底</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中醫話我痾晒有營養既野，出黎做野兩年肥左廿磅，但出街食親飯就痾<br />\n<br />\n中醫聽到我咁痾但無瘦過都笑左笑"},{"pid":"5e7041aa57fd2c2a953dc9480f766644a423c656","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>試下食益生菌，我食左一排由每日痾6，7次減少到痾兩次</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩岩去gnc睇，3百幾蚊一個月，但係唔記得帶會員卡就無買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我求其買一隻，百幾二百蚊到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊度買好？萬寧果d?"},{"pid":"6e68221213e0938083dffa71e8fb34646e6cff05","tid":12912,"uid":30237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:52:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無巴打都有腸易激呀？<br />\n我差唔多次次出街食飯都要搵定廁所咁濟，<br />\n覺得直係好困擾好煩，<br />\n有時又會覺得自己好無用好想喊，<br />\n果次睇醫生問有無藥可以食，點知醫生話無得救，藥都無開比我，<br />\n但係我真係唔想成日咁搵廁所法，<br />\n餐餐都要朋友男友等我<br />\n到底我應該睇腸胃專科定係睇普通家庭醫生先有藥比到我食/改善到？</blockquote><br />\n睇腸胃專科啦 唔係專科其實唔係好識<br />\n<br />\n睇私家腸胃專科啦 公立等一年都唔知有冇得睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇過了，有次腸胃炎到胃痛，走去睇專科+照腸鏡胃鏡咁<br />\n<br />\n有打算遲下再約去睇下有無藥比到我"},{"pid":"38a6dc43870df537090a73e77bcd10a474ed5cb8","tid":12912,"uid":33607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:07:16.000Z","msg":"好多高手"},{"pid":"efeadb5c03c93db9979fa6c3fc1752603d9ddd11","tid":12912,"uid":13754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:45:35.000Z","msg":"我一有壓力右下腹就會有異物感，有啲掩掩痛同幾日先屙次屎，睇醫生都搵唔到原因，剩係開啲消化藥同益生菌，有段時間消化好咗就冇事，而家壓力大咗又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}